The .patch (from https://reviews.apache.org/r/67721/diff/raw/ ) does have the correct author.

@geertjanw should really be in the `.htaccess` with the others I think.  See https://github.com/apache/incubator-netbeans-website/pull/65

I've added the existing link and `https://netbeans.apache.org/nb/report-issue/` - clean URL is probably better for this, but existing one with `.html` should work.

I can't remember where the JBake logs are off-hand - the PR you committed doesn't seem to have built?!
